id: pm-1byt
title: "GH-209: successful pm mutations can exit 13 from unsettled top-level await"
description: "GitHub issue #209 reports successful pm subcommands emitting Node's unsettled top-level await warning from dist/cli.js and exiting 13 after the mutation. Duplicate check: pm search 'unsettled top-level await exit 13 background refresh' found related pm-5rge, but that item is claimed by another agent and tracks broader background-refresh performance integration coverage rather than the exact exit-13 reliability bug. This item covers the narrow awaited unref timer fix and regression coverage."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 1
