author: codex-sdk-cli-agent
parent: pm-mpbb
resolution: Fixed awaited queue-gate backoff timers so successful CLI mutations do not exit 13 from unsettled top-level await.
expected_result: Successful pm commands settle cleanly after awaited background-refresh queue retries.
actual_result: Regression test verified queue-gate timers stay referenced; coverage and manual strict-create workflow passed.
